[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:34,940 --> 00:01:38,950
[Liars in Love]

3
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:41,990
[Episode 21]

4
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:48,270
Watch out for Zhou Yu.

5
00:01:49,990 --> 00:01:50,920
What do you mean?

6
00:01:51,990 --> 00:01:54,430
Zhou Yu's purpose for coming back isn't simple.

7
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:55,310
He probably

8
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,870
came back to

9
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:58,530
avenge his cousin, Zhang Ran.

10
00:01:58,910 --> 00:01:59,680
Zhang Ran?

11
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,880
Who is Ran that Grandpa just mentioned?

12
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,580
His name is Zhang Ran.

13
00:02:08,340 --> 00:02:09,500
He's my uncle's son.

14
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,340
Where is he?

15
00:02:14,550 --> 00:02:15,350
He's dead.

16
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,540
I'm sorry to hear that.

17
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:19,350
He...

18
00:02:19,829 --> 00:02:21,340
We grew up together.

19
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:25,410
He had a car accident
the day before he came back.

20
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,630
Are you filming a cop show or something?

21
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,430
Who's Zhang Ran?

22
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,360
I don't know him.

23
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,590
Zhou Yu is my boyfriend.

24
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:33,250
You shouldn't have said that.

25
00:02:33,350 --> 00:02:34,800
I'm concerned about you.

26
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,210
No, thanks.

27
00:02:39,530 --> 00:02:40,920
I'll find the evidence.

28
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,070
Senior!

29
00:02:47,010 --> 00:02:47,650
Senior!

30
00:02:47,970 --> 00:02:48,860
Are you okay?

31
00:02:50,460 --> 00:02:53,480
[Outpatient]

32
00:02:59,930 --> 00:03:05,060
[Zhou Yu]

33
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,710
Zhou Yu.

34
00:03:17,950 --> 00:03:18,880
Why are you here?

35
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,470
What?

36
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,560
I'm not welcomed?

37
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:21,930
Give it to me.

38
00:03:22,050 --> 00:03:24,590
Grandpa arranged our marriage.

39
00:03:25,070 --> 00:03:26,870
But I just knew he's in hospital.

40
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:28,390
I was being immature.

41
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:30,310
Sometimes grandpa is emotional

42
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:31,090
and can't recognize people.

43
00:03:31,090 --> 00:03:32,710
Just agree with whatever he says.

44
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:34,230
I've volunteered abroad

45
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:36,470
and have dealt with Alzheimer's patients.

46
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:37,200
Don't worry.

47
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:38,680
Okay.

48
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:41,460
Thank you for the fruits.

49
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,300
No need to be so polite.

50
00:03:43,380 --> 00:03:45,040
This gives us some alone time.

51
00:03:45,230 --> 00:03:47,140
Does grandpa usually talk about me with you?

52
00:03:47,140 --> 00:03:48,740
What kind of flowers do you like?

53
00:03:47,510 --> 00:03:50,520
[HONGSHAN HOSPITAL]

54
00:03:57,940 --> 00:03:59,829
[Emergency Room
No Admittance]

55
00:04:04,350 --> 00:04:05,590
Where is my phone?

56
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:08,720
He's in surgery.

57
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:11,410
I think I can make it to the rehabilitation ward.

58
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:27,450
You punk.

59
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:30,080
You've changed your girlfriend
in such a short time?

60
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:30,390
Tell me.

61
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:31,190
Where is Qing?

62
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,000
Grandpa.

63
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,710
I'm Qing.

64
00:04:33,810 --> 00:04:35,130
I am Su Qing.

65
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:36,510
You are Su Qing?

66
00:04:38,350 --> 00:04:39,700
She is indeed Su Qing.

67
00:04:39,730 --> 00:04:40,590
But not the one...

68
00:04:40,590 --> 00:04:41,990
You are Qing.

69
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,320
Sorry.

70
00:04:44,340 --> 00:04:45,909
I have a bad memory.

71
00:04:46,230 --> 00:04:48,350
I can’t remember your face.

72
00:04:48,650 --> 00:04:49,800
It’s OK, Grandpa.

73
00:04:49,909 --> 00:04:50,940
When you are discharged,

74
00:04:50,940 --> 00:04:52,690
I will visit you every day.

75
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:55,159
Then Grandpa won’t forget my face.

76
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:56,650
OK.

77
00:04:57,130 --> 00:04:59,290
Qing, come to visit me

78
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:01,190
more often with this punk.

79
00:05:02,550 --> 00:05:03,350
Punk.

80
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:05,080
You don’t want to come with her?

81
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:06,090
Here, Grandpa.

82
00:05:06,090 --> 00:05:07,020
Have some water.

83
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,480
Grandpa.

84
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:11,110
Zhou Yu wants to come with me.

85
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:13,450
He's just worried I'll be busy with work.

86
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:16,000
But nothing is more important than Grandpa,

87
00:05:16,030 --> 00:05:16,550
right?

88
00:05:17,180 --> 00:05:18,030
Okay.

89
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:19,810
Come.

90
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,290
Punk.

91
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:25,940
You have to treat Qing well.

92
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:41,460
So what's your excuse?

93
00:05:41,460 --> 00:05:44,210
You think I’m conservative,

94
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:46,600
so I don’t want you to marry such a farm girl.

95
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:49,430
Or you colluded with this girl

96
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:51,590
to get the resort development right?

97
00:05:51,590 --> 00:05:52,190
Su,

98
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:53,570
shouldn't we move forward with

99
00:05:53,570 --> 00:05:55,050
our families' arranged marriage?

100
00:05:55,050 --> 00:05:56,560
Don't let him drink.

101
00:05:56,590 --> 00:05:58,230
He can't drink as much as you.

102
00:05:58,710 --> 00:06:01,510
Already starting to care for him before marriage?

103
00:06:02,990 --> 00:06:04,850
We'll be a family sooner or later.

104
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,310
Punk.

105
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:12,620
You have to treat Qing well.

106
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:24,270
Jiang Lai.

107
00:06:25,250 --> 00:06:26,440
I won’t leave you.

108
00:06:27,990 --> 00:06:29,320
No matter what happens,

109
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,590
I'll be with you.

110
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:34,240
Not just because I want to,

111
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:36,390
but because I will.

112
00:06:44,270 --> 00:06:44,870
Jiang Lai.

113
00:06:47,220 --> 00:06:47,780
I’m late.

114
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:55,550
Sorry, Grandpa.

115
00:06:55,550 --> 00:06:56,650
Sorry for barging in.

116
00:06:56,650 --> 00:06:57,500
I’m Jiang Lai.

117
00:06:57,909 --> 00:06:59,470
You wouldn't forget me

118
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:01,100
after just a few days, right?

119
00:07:02,590 --> 00:07:04,920
Grandpa, I have something to tell Zhou Yu.

120
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,950
Grandpa, let’s sit for a while.

121
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,010
Don’t stand there.

122
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,360
Lend me a flower.

123
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:33,190
Maybe I'm being too hasty.

124
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,620
But I still want to ask you.

125
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:38,230
Will you marry me?

126
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:08,570
I'm just kidding.

127
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:14,110
This flower ring is for you, Grandpa.

128
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:15,790
You guys talk.

129
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:16,790
I’m leaving.

130
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,420
Jiang Lai.

131
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:19,670
Jiang Lai.

132
00:08:24,770 --> 00:08:27,140
Why do I think she looks like Qing too?

133
00:08:49,350 --> 00:08:55,090
[Song Biao
I've told you everything I know. What about the thing you promised me?]

134
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:58,790
[Wait for my news]

135
00:09:02,950 --> 00:09:03,670
Tingjiang.

136
00:09:05,070 --> 00:09:05,830
Chairman.

137
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:07,270
I heard you're sick.

138
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:08,390
I'm...

139
00:09:08,410 --> 00:09:09,020
I'm fine.

140
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:10,130
Just appendicitis.

141
00:09:10,130 --> 00:09:11,060
A minor surgery.

142
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:12,320
It's not a minor surgery.

143
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,000
Let me see.

144
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:14,860
It's okay.

145
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,670
I think it's not

146
00:09:21,350 --> 00:09:23,630
quite perfect.

147
00:09:28,190 --> 00:09:28,950
Feels good?

148
00:09:33,890 --> 00:09:35,010
What do you mean?

149
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,910
Sun Wei has told me about

150
00:09:42,930 --> 00:09:44,660
what happened between you two.

151
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:53,280
There's nothing

152
00:09:53,710 --> 00:09:55,640
between Vice President Sun and me.

153
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,470
Room 1818 in Weiheng Hotel.

154
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:04,340
What does this mean?

155
00:10:18,010 --> 00:10:19,600
Your check-in records are all here.

156
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:21,470
[Weiheng Hotel Reservation List of Li Tingjiang and Sun Wei]

157
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,740
Take a look.

158
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,920
How do you explain it?

159
00:10:32,590 --> 00:10:33,690
No need to explain.

160
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,880
What are you going to do to me?

161
00:10:37,760 --> 00:10:40,170
Are you so brazen about having an affair?

162
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:42,240
And you dared to do this to me.

163
00:10:45,370 --> 00:10:46,920
I have 100 ways

164
00:10:47,340 --> 00:10:49,460
to make you two disappear.

165
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,120
Now,

166
00:10:52,430 --> 00:10:54,560
I'll get you a more comfortable place.

167
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:00,880
There's a man named Song Biao.

168
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:02,610
Do you know him?

169
00:11:15,290 --> 00:11:17,540
He kidnapped Su Qing a while ago

170
00:11:19,010 --> 00:11:22,570
and demanded ransom from Vice President Sun.

171
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,870
I have him now.

172
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:29,720
He told me all the good deeds

173
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:31,680
he did for you in the past few years.

174
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:37,340
Including a car accident.

175
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,710
I think you planned it.

176
00:11:41,010 --> 00:11:42,740
How dare you threaten me.

177
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:44,750
I dare not.

178
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:51,200
I'll give you one last chance.

179
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,540
Where is Song Biao?

180
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:54,300
I can't tell you.

181
00:11:55,710 --> 00:11:57,310
He won't be safe if I tell you.

182
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:00,900
At least I know

183
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,520
he is safe now.

184
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:17,780
Zhou Yu.

185
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:18,310
You dumb!

186
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:21,190
I'll beat you to death!

187
00:12:21,350 --> 00:12:22,020
Bad man!

188
00:12:31,470 --> 00:12:32,190
Maybe

189
00:12:32,350 --> 00:12:34,630
I'm being too hasty.

190
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,900
But I still want to ask you.

191
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:39,440
Will you marry me?

192
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:51,880
I’m sorry.

193
00:13:16,590 --> 00:13:17,650
Jiang Lai, come in.

194
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,550
It’s OK. You go first.

195
00:13:18,550 --> 00:13:19,550
I'll take the next one.

196
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:20,480
No time, no time!

197
00:13:42,570 --> 00:13:44,090
Jiang Lai, I’m sorry.

198
00:13:44,210 --> 00:13:46,410
I was in a hurry to get into the elevator.

199
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,230
It's okay.

200
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,210
Chen Jun.

201
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:56,600
Did you skip breakfast?

202
00:13:57,180 --> 00:13:57,930
Me?

203
00:14:00,230 --> 00:14:00,960
Yes, yes.

204
00:14:01,090 --> 00:14:03,690
I forgot to have breakfast this morning.

205
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,860
You have to eat your breakfast.

206
00:14:05,860 --> 00:14:06,610
Got it?

207
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:07,920
Okay.

208
00:14:07,950 --> 00:14:08,750
Thanks, Boss.

209
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:23,750
Boss.

210
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:24,530
Here we are.

211
00:14:47,610 --> 00:14:48,240
Everyone,

212
00:14:48,510 --> 00:14:50,000
Mr. Zhou treats us to breakfast.

213
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:50,860
Come and get it.

214
00:14:51,470 --> 00:14:52,880
Thanks, Boss.

215
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:54,370
Thanks, Mr. Zhou.

216
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:09,690
Mr. Zhou.

217
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:13,070
What is this?

218
00:15:14,140 --> 00:15:17,070
Jiang Lai was distributing breakfast in the office.

219
00:15:18,490 --> 00:15:20,200
I mean what’s in the folder?

220
00:15:21,990 --> 00:15:24,070
I need your signature.

221
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:31,930
Mr. Zhou.

222
00:15:31,950 --> 00:15:33,680
Did you quarrel with Jiang Lai?

223
00:15:33,910 --> 00:15:34,470
No.

224
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:38,780
It's normal for a couple to quarrel occasionally.

225
00:15:38,780 --> 00:15:40,970
It just takes one person to take a step,

226
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:43,230
and then 80% of problems can be solved.

227
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,430
I told you.

228
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:45,560
We didn't.

229
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:51,730
I know men can't swallow their pride sometimes,

230
00:15:52,230 --> 00:15:55,940
but it's better than losing your girlfriend.

231
00:15:55,990 --> 00:15:56,570
Right?

232
00:15:58,460 --> 00:16:00,780
If you find it hard to be alone with her,

233
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:02,270
you can arrange group activities

234
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,550
to create opportunities.

235
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:04,950
Then it won't be awkward.

236
00:16:06,710 --> 00:16:08,430
I think you're too idle.

237
00:16:08,950 --> 00:16:10,950
Go and re-organize all the investment documents

238
00:16:10,950 --> 00:16:11,990
of the resort.

239
00:16:12,670 --> 00:16:14,200
I want to see the latest one.

240
00:16:23,430 --> 00:16:25,960
You really don't need me to organize a dinner?

241
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:47,690
Nice weather today.

242
00:16:47,790 --> 00:16:49,300
Look at the clouds outside.

243
00:16:49,300 --> 00:16:50,310
What's going on?

244
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:52,960
She sat down as soon as she saw me.

245
00:16:52,980 --> 00:16:54,420
I couldn't stop her.

246
00:16:54,550 --> 00:16:55,250
What now?

247
00:16:58,620 --> 00:16:59,710
I'm going to the bathroom.

248
00:16:59,710 --> 00:17:00,090
OK.

249
00:17:05,690 --> 00:17:07,089
When is Jiang Lai coming?

250
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:10,710
She should be here if everything goes well.

251
00:17:14,750 --> 00:17:15,950
Chen Jun.

252
00:17:15,950 --> 00:17:17,730
You only tell Jiang Lai when there's good food.

253
00:17:17,730 --> 00:17:19,640
Why are you here?

254
00:17:20,990 --> 00:17:21,750
Can’t I?

255
00:17:22,069 --> 00:17:22,670
Jiang Lai.

256
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:24,369
I want to talk to you.

257
00:17:29,630 --> 00:17:30,440
Jiang Lai.

258
00:17:31,590 --> 00:17:32,390
What a coincidence.

259
00:17:32,390 --> 00:17:33,920
You're here for dinner too?

260
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:37,800
Yes.

261
00:17:38,980 --> 00:17:40,070
I suddenly want to eat noodles.

262
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,110
Let's go eat noodles.

263
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:41,510
Okay.

264
00:17:41,510 --> 00:17:41,910
Let's go.

265
00:17:41,910 --> 00:17:42,420
Sorry for interrupting.

266
00:17:42,420 --> 00:17:43,100
Enjoy.

267
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:50,750
What are we

268
00:17:50,770 --> 00:17:51,500
going to eat?

269
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:04,510
Sorry.

270
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:06,810
I was too hasty.

271
00:18:06,890 --> 00:18:08,290
I just want to talk to you.

272
00:18:08,980 --> 00:18:10,710
There's nothing to talk about.

273
00:18:13,990 --> 00:18:15,280
You mean what I said the other day?

274
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:16,040
I was joking.

275
00:18:16,070 --> 00:18:17,530
I know you were not joking.

276
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:21,840
I admit

277
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:24,270
I hesitated that day.

278
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,190
But it's not because I don't want to marry you.

279
00:18:26,190 --> 00:18:27,120
It's because...

280
00:18:31,530 --> 00:18:33,170
It's because I have some matters

281
00:18:32,700 --> 00:18:35,900
♫The bitterness lingers in my heart♫

282
00:18:33,390 --> 00:18:34,120
to deal with.

283
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:36,050
I don't want to get you involved.

284
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:39,500
♫The hidden wound♫

285
00:18:39,950 --> 00:18:42,310
♫The emotions are slipping away♫

286
00:18:40,620 --> 00:18:41,440
It's okay.

287
00:18:41,900 --> 00:18:42,990
You can take your time.

288
00:18:42,990 --> 00:18:46,800
♫Should I try to hold on♫

289
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:45,450
It has nothing to do with me.

290
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,350
It has nothing to do with you?

291
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:49,660
