584
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:27,080
I know a lot about him.

585
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:29,820
He won't do anything to me for a while.

586
00:35:30,440 --> 00:35:31,200
That's good.

587
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:33,220
By the way,

588
00:35:33,590 --> 00:35:34,670
why are you here?

589
00:35:35,410 --> 00:35:36,610
Do you know Jiang Lai?

590
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:40,990
I went to deliver something to Zhou Yu a few days ago.

591
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:42,790
Jiang Lai was the only one there.

592
00:35:42,890 --> 00:35:44,080
My appendix has burst again.

593
00:35:44,080 --> 00:35:45,480
So she sent me to the hospital.

594
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:46,840
I came here to thank her.

595
00:35:48,390 --> 00:35:49,250
Appendicitis?

596
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:50,740
Why didn't I know?

597
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,510
I'm good now.

598
00:35:51,540 --> 00:35:52,270
I'm good now.

599
00:35:53,900 --> 00:35:54,560
Tingjiang.

600
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:56,070
Let's leave here, okay?

601
00:35:56,440 --> 00:35:58,670
Let's take Zhen to America.

602
00:35:58,710 --> 00:35:59,830
Let's start over.

603
00:36:00,290 --> 00:36:01,210
Sun Wei,

604
00:36:01,740 --> 00:36:03,200
don't be naive.

605
00:36:03,550 --> 00:36:06,810
The issue with Song Biao kidnapping Su Qing isn't over yet.

606
00:36:07,480 --> 00:36:08,740
Give me some more time.

607
00:36:09,130 --> 00:36:11,060
Song Biao just wants money, right?

608
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:12,700
I've already bought the apartment

609
00:36:12,700 --> 00:36:14,510
we stayed in for vacation in America.

610
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:15,970
I put all of our money here.

611
00:36:21,830 --> 00:36:23,670
Take care of Song Biao as soon as possible.

612
00:36:23,670 --> 00:36:25,200
Let's leave here together.

613
00:36:26,240 --> 00:36:27,500
Where is the bathroom?

614
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:34,130
Who?

615
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:11,130
What's wrong, honey?

616
00:37:11,130 --> 00:37:11,860
Are you okay?

617
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:13,320
Chen Jun.

618
00:37:13,350 --> 00:37:14,620
There's a spider.

619
00:37:14,710 --> 00:37:15,510
A pig?

620
00:37:16,100 --> 00:37:16,710
Where?

621
00:37:16,730 --> 00:37:17,660
Where's the pig?

622
00:37:17,660 --> 00:37:18,460
What's wrong?

623
00:37:18,830 --> 00:37:19,910
A pig?

624
00:37:20,330 --> 00:37:20,970
Pig?

625
00:37:22,990 --> 00:37:23,870
Well.

626
00:37:23,990 --> 00:37:25,290
Yiyi came over to look for the bathroom

627
00:37:25,290 --> 00:37:27,890
and she got scared when she saw a little spider.

628
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:29,410
No!

629
00:37:37,060 --> 00:37:37,860
The spider...

630
00:37:37,900 --> 00:37:39,380
The spider is so big.

631
00:37:39,410 --> 00:37:40,610
It's not little.

632
00:37:45,310 --> 00:37:45,830
Mr. Zhou.

633
00:37:45,830 --> 00:37:46,830
Your clothes...

634
00:37:47,330 --> 00:37:48,800
I was changing my clothes.

635
00:37:48,830 --> 00:37:50,040
I heard someone calling outside.

636
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:51,770
I thought something happened.

637
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:53,640
I'll go back and finish changing.

638
00:37:55,290 --> 00:37:56,290
Yu.

639
00:37:57,190 --> 00:37:59,250
Why is the scar on your shoulder gone?

640
00:37:59,340 --> 00:38:00,100
I found it.

641
00:38:03,060 --> 00:38:04,870
Sorry, Yu.

642
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:06,120
It's okay.

643
00:38:06,150 --> 00:38:07,080
It doesn't hurt.

644
00:38:07,870 --> 00:38:08,800
Don't be scared.

645
00:38:08,860 --> 00:38:10,060
This is our secret.

646
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:15,860
What scar?

647
00:38:16,330 --> 00:38:17,480
When I was little,

648
00:38:17,510 --> 00:38:18,900
Yu got hit on the back

649
00:38:19,020 --> 00:38:21,060
to save me.

650
00:38:21,650 --> 00:38:23,150
There was a big scar.

651
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,800
Strange.

652
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:26,510
Why is it gone now?

653
00:38:27,950 --> 00:38:28,790
That's because I...

654
00:38:28,790 --> 00:38:29,450
Whatever it is,

655
00:38:29,450 --> 00:38:31,080
hurry up and put on your clothes.

656
00:38:31,080 --> 00:38:33,540
We don't have much cold medicine at the farm.

657
00:38:34,860 --> 00:38:35,390
Okay.

658
00:38:39,970 --> 00:38:40,350
Let's go.

659
00:38:40,350 --> 00:38:41,190
I'll take you to the bathroom.
